        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>The City of uMhlathuze, as a port city, will offer improved quality of life for all its citizens through sustainable development. It will be a renowned centre for: Trade, Tourism and Nature-lovers, Coastal Recreation, Commerce, Industry, Forestry, and Agriculture.</p>
